    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="https://philadelphia.craigslist.org/apa/d/norristown-furnished-farmhouse/7517134020.html"></div>
        </div>
"THE HEARTHSIDE," A TASTEFULLY DECORATED ONE-BEDROOM APARTMENT IN A COLONIAL FARMHOUSE, IS NOW AVAILABLE AT HISTORIC LILYFIELD FARM!    <br>
<br>
LilyField Farm, a 300-year-old historic farmstead, is a hidden treasure of unique accommodations.  The farmhouse features two fully furnished and updated executive apartments: the Hearthside and the Smokehouse.  The one-bedroom Hearthside features a delightful sunroom and the original colonial walk-in fireplace. The two-bedroom Smokehouse (not currently available) features a lakeside view through sliding glass doors that open onto a private porch.<br>
 <br>
A picture, as they say, is worth a thousand words. You can quickly see why we love living at LilyField Farm   and why you might, too! These restored and updated accommodations are value-priced and a welcome relief from cookie-cutter complexes and pricey corporate suites. <br>
<br>
This is ideal for executive relocation, internships, traveling health care workers, health care professionals, term-contract employees, job relocation, corporate housing needs, students, transitional housing, or temporary housing for insurance company clients. Short term, and year-to-year options are available. <br>
<br>
 LilyField is a working Pennsylvania farmstead nestled on a hillside overlooking a lake. It's a tranquil place where blue herons glide just above the water, and turtles sunbathe to a chorus of bullfrogs. The pastures are animated by chickens, ducks, goats, a peacock named Bo Diddley, and our two potbellied pigs stretched out under the apple trees for their afternoon nap amid a glory of over 250 varieties of daylilies and other blossoms. <br>
<br>
We look forward to talking with you soon!<br>
<br>
Suzanne Lord  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/phi/apa/7517134020/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
<br>
 and Bob Sheasley   <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/phi/apa/7517134020/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
